</taxonomicName>
was found in the depth interval of 
<quantity id="93599B2CFFC1FF592100FE32FBFCFE26" box="[1037,1137,398,424]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.85" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="1.7" pageId="15" pageNumber="562" unit="m" value="18.5" valueMax="20.0" valueMin="17.0">17–20 m</quantity>
on rock bottoms. Females with developed oostegites were detected in both localities in July.
</paragraph>
