</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="1CBB6542FFC1FF5925CAFDA2FE66FD0E" pageId="15" pageNumber="562" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="541E36C9FFC1FF5925CAFDA2FE66FD0E" blockId="15.[151,1437,325,640]" pageId="15" pageNumber="562">
<emphasis id="66D5EADBFFC1FF5925CAFDA2FEB9FDB6" bold="true" box="[199,308,542,568]" pageId="15" pageNumber="562">Remarks</emphasis>
. The specimen of 
<taxonomicName id="93A14D4AFFC1FF592701FDA2FCD4FDB6" authorityName="Labay" authorityYear="2018" box="[524,857,542,568]" class="Malacostraca" family="Pleustidae" genus="Cognateosymtes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="15" pageNumber="562" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="serraticoxae">
<emphasis id="66D5EADBFFC1FF592701FDA2FCD4FDB6" box="[524,857,542,568]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="562">Cognateosymtes serraticoxae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from shallow waters off southeastern 
<collectingRegion id="9665F82BFFC1FF59201EFDA2FAF8FDB6" box="[1299,1397,542,568]" country="Russia" name="Sakhalin" pageId="15" pageNumber="562">Sakhalin</collectingRegion>
Island are morphologically completely identical to specimens of the 
<typeStatus id="8B1A886BFFC1FF59268FFDFEFC3FFDD2" box="[898,946,578,604]" pageId="15" pageNumber="562">type</typeStatus>
series from coastal waters off southwestern 
<collectingRegion id="9665F82BFFC1FF59259AFDDAFF74FD0E" box="[151,249,614,640]" country="Russia" name="Sakhalin" pageId="15" pageNumber="562">Sakhalin</collectingRegion>
Island (
<bibRefCitation id="30304B38FFC1FF59245EFDDAFE52FD0E" author="Labay, V. S." box="[339,479,614,640]" pageId="15" pageNumber="562" pagination="220 - 230" refId="ref6589" refString="Labay, V. S. (2018) Cognateosymtes serraticoxae, new genus, new species, a pleustid amphipod from the Sea of Japan (Crustacea: Amphipoda: Gammaridea: Pleustidae: Eosymtinae). Zootax a, 4521 (2), 220 - 230. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4521.2.4" type="journal article" year="2018">Labay 2018</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
